 = a sin(t) + b cos(t) - w sin(t)cos(t)。<br />\n因此，短邊的最大可能值是 min{d(t) | 0 &le; t &le; &pi;/2}。求取得 d 的極小值的 t 不難，只要解 d'(t) = 0 便可。此方程可改寫成一組以 tan(t) 為變數的四次方程，不太難解。"},{"pid":"94307ae80e38e9e551f31f39e901f514c37448b4","tid":1007780,"uid":52817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc9df5a20cc9be121e7fa2b49308d3bbb9f52438","tid":1007780,"uid":184509,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T06:35:51.000Z","msg":"咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jjeyszO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjjeyszO.jpg&h=82288ded&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T07:29:58.000Z","msg":"你畫番條tunnel係外圍，果兩條線唔係平行於AB，所以長過AB都轉到。"},{"pid":"29cbe1d28ff21f6545a594c49cea08adcdf29865","tid":1007780,"uid":46500,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T08:35:52.000Z","msg":"sofa problem<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes10.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes10.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n數學未解難題wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2f5b400458971444127487012ec8e243955a4ef","tid":1007780,"uid":219990,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T08:41:05.000Z","msg":"八千轉，兩米車"},{"pid":"5c6435cd941002684c3a123a083e2ba3866ebe9e","tid":1007780,"uid":175298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T04:51:31.000Z","msg":"係就apply得盡啲，3d"},{"pid":"20e1ed8095839a35179f0fdbe60ac63ca4075f09","tid":1007780,"uid":61577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c6435cd941002684c3a123a083e2ba3866ebe9e","tid":1007780,"uid":175298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T04:51:31.000Z","msg":"係就apply得盡啲，3d"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T07:07:04.000Z","msg":"唔明"},{"pid":"c3a37e4f6fce924cc2c7013b8a4249facab76194","tid":1007780,"uid":61577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"p